    "Proposed schemeIn this section, a scheme is proposed to ensure the efficient and secure storage and sharing of patient EMRs.",
    "In the proposed scheme, a document-oriented database and a blockchain structure are used together.",
    "Whereas the patient EMRs are kept in the encrypted distributed database, the blockchain is used to ensure data integrity and security in Fig. 2 Blockchain structure accessing the data.",
